    "To address this, BDD100K has developed a configurable annotation system that supports these three types of annotations.",
    "Furthermore, BDD100K has introduced improvements to enhance annotation efficiency and has collected efficient full-frame semantic instance segmentation.",
    "The dataset is more challenging compared to existing benchmarks for driving image recognition because it covers more realistic driving scenarios and captures a \"long-tail\" distribution of classes with varying appearances and poses in different environmental domains.",
